modName: Gasmist Cove - A Forsworn Type Cove
summary: Ever seen Robbers Cove? Gasmist Cove is like it. It has safe chests, 4 weapon rackets and full smithing equipment.
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=green]Gasmist Cove - [/color]

Gasmist Cove looks like one of those wooden little forts that the bandist have (Robbers Cove for example), but has more than those can provide. It has a cellar which is locked (The key is on the table where alchemy and ench. benches are at), 4 safe chests (Armor, weapon, ingredient and food chests), 4 weapon rackets and 3 towers.

[color=crimson]Future updates:[/color]

-Guards or friendly bandits that patrol the surrounding (and by patrol I mean stand around on the guard towers)
-Decorations

Compatibility issues:
None. [/b]
author: SleyorV
